    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>This would break BC but phpseclib's Crypt_RSA seems much more feature packed then the RSA implementation in ZF. PEAR's own Crypt_RSA has deprecated itself in favor of phpseclib's implementation.</p>

<p>Among other features phpseclib's Crypt_RSA supports...  more key formats, key conversion, PSS signing and OAEP encryption.</p>

